THOUGHT: I need to follow the required steps in order: search news for signals, find contacts, score ICP fit, save contact, and draft email. Let me start with searching for recent news about Expedia.

ACTION: search_news
ARGS: {"company": "Expedia"}

THOUGHT: Great signals found - Expedia has new B2B leadership (Alfonso Paredes as President, B2B & CCO), strong Q1 profitability, AI investments, and B2B expansion acceleration. Now I need to search for contacts in their organization.

ACTION: search_contacts
ARGS: {"domain": "expedia.com"}

THOUGHT: Good contacts found. Eric Hart (Chief Strategy, Business, and Corporate Development Officer) is the best fit given the B2B expansion signals and strategic initiatives. Now I need to score the ICP fit based on the signals I found.

ACTION: score_icp
ARGS: {"account_id": "expedia-group", "reasoning": "Expedia is implementing major AI overhaul with significant compute cost investments, experiencing record Q1 profitability with 15% revenue growth, launching B2B expansion with new CCO Alfonso Paredes, and actively scaling business development initiatives. Strong fit for enterprise software/AI infrastructure solutions targeting travel/hospitality tech leaders."}

THOUGHT: Good ICP score of 0.75. Now I need to save Eric Hart as the best contact given his Chief Strategy role aligns with B2B expansion and strategic initiatives.

ACTION: save_contact
ARGS: {"account_id": "expedia-group", "name": "Eric Hart", "title": "Chief Strategy, Business, and Corporate Development Officer", "email": "eric.hart@expedia.com"}

THOUGHT: Contact saved successfully. Now I need to draft a personalized email using the signals I found: AI overhaul, B2B expansion with new CCO, record profitability, and strategic growth initiatives.

ACTION: draft_email
ARGS: {"contact_name": "Eric Hart", "title": "Chief Strategy, Business, and Corporate Development Officer", "company": "Expedia Group", "signal": "Expedia announced record Q1 2026 profitability with 15% revenue growth, major AI compute infrastructure investments, and B2B expansion acceleration under new President Alfonso Paredes. Company is scaling strategic initiatives across AI-powered travel and B2B partnerships.", "sender_context": "GTM Prospect Agent researching enterprise solutions for high-growth travel tech companies undergoing AI transformation"}
